Privacy Policy

Last updated: February 2026

1. Information We Collect

Personal Information:
- Apple ID authentication token 
- Inventory items you manually enter
- Chat messages you send to AI assistant
- Technical information automatically transmitted 
  during app operation, including IP address and 
  in-app language setting

2. How We Use Your Information

The Uses of the collected information are:
- Authenticate your identity via Apple Sign In
- Store and manage your personal inventory
- Process AI chat requests via OpenAI API
- May review usage patterns and user interactions 
   to improve app features and user experience

3. Information Sharing

We share data with:
- OpenAI LLC: Chat messages processed by OpenAI API
- Amazon Web Services: Secure data storage
- Apple Inc: Authentication services

We do not sell your personal data. If we introduce 
advertising in future versions, we will update this 
policy and notify users accordingly.


4. Data Storage

Your data is stored on:
- AWS DynamoDB servers (encrypted at rest)
- Your device (inventory images stored locally)

Server logs containing IP addresses and technical 
information are retained for security and debugging 
purposes for as long as necessary.
We implement reasonable security measures to 
protect your personal information from unauthorized 
access, disclosure, or destruction.

5. Data Retention

We retain your data for as long as:
- Your account remains active
- Required by law

6. Your Rights

Right to data deletion: You may request deletion of your account and associated data by contacting us at [clbrks@outlook.com]. 
Please allow up to 30 days for processing.

You have the right to:
- Access your personal data
- Request account and data deletion by contacting us

7. Children's Privacy

This app is intended for users aged 13 and older. 
We do not knowingly collect personal information 
from users under 13. If we become aware that a 
user under 13 has provided personal information, 
we will take steps to delete such information promptly.

8. Changes to This Policy

We may update this policy periodically.
Continued use of the app after changes
constitutes acceptance of the new policy.

9. Contact Us

For privacy questions or data deletion requests:
[clbrks@outlook.com]

10. Third Party Services

OpenAI Privacy Policy:
https://openai.com/privacy

Apple Privacy Policy:
https://www.apple.com/privacy/

AWS Privacy Policy:
https://aws.amazon.com/privacy/
